features: Dual-sided magnifying makeup mirror: One side features a clear 1x flat mirror, while the other side offers a 5x magnification mirror, designed specifically for individuals with myopia and those seeking precision. Ideal for wearing contact lenses, applying makeup, shaving, skincare, and more

Portable and compact: Whether for travel or everyday use, this magnifying mirror with stand is incredibly portable and compact. With dimensions of just 4.5 inches and weighing only 9 ounces, it conveniently fits into your handbag or backpack, allowing you to take it with you wherever you go

High-quality materials: This magnifying travel mirror is crafted with top-notch materials, featuring a beautiful silver frame with a glossy surface, showcasing a stylish and attractive appearance. Moreover, we have specifically chosen materials that are waterproof, rust-resistant, and corrosion-resistant, ensuring the product's durability and longevity

Whether used as a tabletop mirror, carried on the go, or hung on the wall, this travel mirror with magnification is extremely versatile. It is suitable for various settings, including bathrooms, bedrooms, offices, dressing rooms, eyewear stores, hotels, and more

Usage caution: For optimal usage, it is recommended to maintain a distance of 15 centimeters or less between the small magnifying mirror and your eyes to prevent image distortion and dizziness. If you experience any blurriness or lack of clarity, you can gradually adjust the distance until the image becomes clear
